        {
            "title": "警方寶達邨打擊街頭聚賭 拘12人包括長者",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警方寶達邨打擊街頭聚賭 拘12人包括長者\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1927f70dc0d660d80bae52587266ad75/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250309/_2025030923250785312.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警方寶達邨打擊街頭聚賭 拘12人包括長者</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（3月9日）晚上9時許，警方於秀茂坪區內街頭聚賭黑點巡查，期間在寶達邨拘捕12人。據了解被捕人多為長者，最年長為76歲。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方過去曾提醒市民，根據香港法例第148章 《賭博條例》，任何人在賭場以外任何場所進行賭博屬違法行為，一經定罪，最高罰款為五萬港元及監禁九個月。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128445/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"被捕人被帶上警車。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5064bce130db12160894d1a40b9fbb1a/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-0922_30_59_aae2a453.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        被捕人被帶上警車。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
