        {
            "title": "Ian出發倫敦展開巡唱  食健身餐帶定背心隨時著上台  致敬方大同環節 : 拭目以待",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Ian於今晚啟程出發到倫敦為演出作準備。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/22135f67e71f7644c53d05e88db7cd67/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250309/_2025030922484165913.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Ian於今晚啟程出發到倫敦為演出作準備。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>男團MIRROR首位展開海外巡唱的成員陳卓賢（Ian），將於3月12日在倫敦OVO Arena Wembley為其《IAN CHAN “TEARS” IN MY SIGHT SOLO CONCERT 2025》作演出，Ian於今晚啟程出發到倫敦為演出作準備，大批Ian粉絲「Hellosss」早已聞風而至，約有百多人手執燈牌和應援手幅在VIP通道守候他的現身，迫爆機場方面劃設的粉絲區域，亦有十數人選擇在馬路對面遠觀Ian，機場亦派出保安和職員維持秩序，亦有航空公司職員在現場作安排。Ian於晚上9時45分乘七人車現身VIP通道入口，在他現身前已有兩位助手現場守候，戴cap帽和口罩的Ian見到大批Hellosss在場打氣，以揮手和鞠躬回應大家的熱情，亦大方企定定讓傳媒和粉絲影相。\n\n</p><h2>陳卓賢為新歌拍MV吹足一日風</h2>\n<p>Ian接受訪問，問到出發到首站倫敦心情如何？他表示：「緊張呀！少少壓力，巡唱第一場希望做到120分給大家看。」他又指最近休息得麻麻地，日前氣溫急降下拍攝MV，要在山頂及海邊等戶外作拍攝，因此也吹了整日風，但身體狀況OK，只是喉嚨有點乾，因此也盡量休息保持最佳狀態。Ian近日頻頻做Gym，問到肌肉狀態如何？他笑言：「OK呀！未到巔峰，大家都關注會不會穿背心，我的回答是到當地看天氣吧，因為好凍呀，我有帶定背心，不是很佔位置，咁少布係咪？到時看情況。」他形容現在的肌肉是7分，和香港演唱時差不多，也自覺最近消瘦些，可能上台時比較顯線條，「因為我比較白，如果膚色深些可以更好看，否則燈打下來會比較浮腫。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"大批Ian粉絲「Hellosss」早已聞風而至，約有百多人手執燈牌和應援手幅在VIP通道守候他的現身。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0d37bf598d3de401f797961e47790497/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0149.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大批Ian粉絲「Hellosss」早已聞風而至，約有百多人手執燈牌和應援手幅在VIP通道守候他的現身。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"亦有十數人選擇在馬路對面遠觀Ian，機場亦派出保安和職員維持秩序。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/067c7250337a33f6b07b36540cf86d6a/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0151.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        亦有十數人選擇在馬路對面遠觀Ian，機場亦派出保安和職員維持秩序。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian於晚上9時45分乘七人車現身VIP通道入口。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bbe935aa51c8d9b683acf6ebf9b98471/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0152.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian於晚上9時45分乘七人車現身VIP通道入口。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"戴cap帽和口罩的Ian現身。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ea3c4eade51d67d287a1eb473648b405/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0154.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戴cap帽和口罩的Ian現身。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian見到大批Hellosss在場打氣，以揮手和鞠躬回應大家的熱情。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4b1962a2ed6771417f7a69d837e18be3/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0155.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian見到大批Hellosss在場打氣，以揮手和鞠躬回應大家的熱情。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian亦大方企定定讓傳媒和粉絲影相。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/27c15a430df976ab2313d5203351226a/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0156.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian亦大方企定定讓傳媒和粉絲影相。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian將於3月12日在倫敦OVO Arena Wembley為其《IAN CHAN “TEARS” IN MY SIGHT SOLO CONCERT 2025》作演出\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d099c68335e4588344defc9c241e69c2/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0157.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian將於3月12日在倫敦OVO Arena Wembley為其《IAN CHAN “TEARS” IN MY SIGHT SOLO CONCERT 2025》作演出\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"問到出發到首站倫敦心情如何？他表示：「緊張呀！少少壓力。」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e829aaf11065fb33cf1a0c30f3017330/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0158.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        問到出發到首站倫敦心情如何？他表示：「緊張呀！少少壓力。」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>歌單會有變動兼有新衫</h2>\n<p>問到歌單，Ian形容是有小驚喜的，要看歌迷收不收貨，可能會有新歌，造型方面也有新衫，和監製細榮緊密聯繫。Ian笑指最掛念愛犬雞脾，見到他有點SAD和不安，相信只是一段小日子。Ian自爆長途機比較難睡覺，因此也帶備了褪黑素助眠，希望這幾日可以好好休息準備，笑言要維持身型，飛機餐也不敢食，自爆近日都食健身餐。提到拍MV是否有新作品很快推出？他指最近進入後期，會有小修改，相信很快便和大家見面，希望歌迷喜歡新歌，預告是自己創作，是特別的風格。他又透露帶了樂器出發，會繼續彈樂器取靈感，說不定會有「Made in London」的新作。談到Ian也喜歡方大同，問到倫敦站會否有致敬環節？Ian賣關子道：「拭目以待！」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian希望巡唱第一場希望做到120分給大家看。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e7eddb9711e916fcde462a1cd1ec643c/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0161.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian希望巡唱第一場希望做到120分給大家看。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"不少Hellosss高呼「加油」、「等你返嚟」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/abfb42c2d0bca82b92ee248dae142cce/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0162.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        不少Hellosss高呼「加油」、「等你返嚟」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian近日頻頻做Gym，問到肌肉狀態如何？他笑言：「OK呀！未到巔峰。」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3a314da42cabc110287f188ddfe7e783/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0163.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian近日頻頻做Gym，問到肌肉狀態如何？他笑言：「OK呀！未到巔峰。」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"問到歌單，Ian形容是有小驚喜的，要看歌迷收不收貨，可能會有新歌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03137a0e68b0379a6aa610710434a3ae/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0164.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        問到歌單，Ian形容是有小驚喜的，要看歌迷收不收貨，可能會有新歌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian笑指最掛念愛犬雞脾，見到他有點SAD和不安，相信只是一段小日子。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c6bb6cd4989c573b39a231cd60cd9e79/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0165.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian笑指最掛念愛犬雞脾，見到他有點SAD和不安，相信只是一段小日子。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian自爆長途機比較難睡覺，因此也帶備了褪黑素助眠，希望這幾日可以好好休息準備。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68e7994909236d8b279567ea94590c80/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0166.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian自爆長途機比較難睡覺，因此也帶備了褪黑素助眠，希望這幾日可以好好休息準備。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian笑言要維持身型，飛機餐也不敢食。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cebf9f3c526a91c6def7d7197b616cdc/2025-03/IMG-20250309-WA0167.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian笑言要維持身型，飛機餐也不敢食。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian又透露帶了樂器出發，會繼續彈樂器取靈感，說不定會有「Made in London」的新作。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2f00abf5fa21bd21cee718285422e21b/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-16_at_17_13_48.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian又透露帶了樂器出發，會繼續彈樂器取靈感，說不定會有「Made in London」的新作。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian有帶定背心，至於會否著上台就要到時看情況。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9510272846b29c1272086e9c2c23ed28/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-16_at_17_13_49.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian有帶定背心，至於會否著上台就要到時看情況。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>Ian完騷留當地與家姐共聚</h2>\n<p>Ian表示完騷後會留在當地放假一下，透露姊姊的家庭在當地，上一次見面已是其7月演唱會，姐姐和家人回來欣賞，「今次我過去他們主場，可以探他們，陪陪家人幾日。」不過4月演出家人就未能回來欣賞，因為小朋友需要上學。問到姨甥可有仰慕他？Ian笑說：「最小的只有4歲，他們說舅父仔做的事好犀利、好難呀！要上台唱歌好難，講話好可愛，好支持我，會傳短訊叫我加油。而大仔也有傳短訊給我，說今次不去睇騷了，因為太夜，不想隔天上學請假，我幾欣賞他的態度，好誠實，所以我好尊重他們決定，哈哈！」\n\n</p>\n<p>訪問完成後，Hellosss高呼「加油」、「等你返嚟」，Ian亦走近粉絲合照，邊揮手邊步入VIP區內。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
